INSERT INTO "review" (title,text,date,movie_id,user_id) VALUES ('A living masterpiece ', 'This is truly one of the best Disney movies ever. I really enjoyed it when I first seen it, about when I was 6, and since then I watched it over and over again. I simply LOOOOVED the music. Its one of the best soundtracks Ive ever heard. And, speaking of soundtrack, I just cant tell in words how much I love the song Can You Feel The Love Tonight. Is one of my favorite songs ever. I truly believe that this motion picture could easily be nominated for The Best Picture, but The Best Song and the Best Original Score is really enough. I wonder if they will ever think to make a prequel of this movie in order to understand who is Mufasa, Scar, Sarabi and the other characters. In short, this movie will be remembered in the next 100 years. Truly.','2021-01-01 22:04:11.245091',1,3);
